SIMPLE: reconsider
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reconsider
<hw>Re`con*sid"er</hw> <pr>(r?`k?n*s?d"?r)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>To consider again; <as>as, to <ex>reconsider</ex> a
subject</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Parliamentary Practice)</fld> <def>To take up for
renewed consideration, as a motion or a vote which has been previously
acted upon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reconsideration</ent>⟦br⟧
